\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

 is not a unit in 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{1}$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $f\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

